### convertion

Convert all .doc, .docx, .xls, .xlsx, .ppt, and .pptx files to PDF(s) in the current directory.

#### install it via (pip/pip3):
```
pip install convertion
```

#### execute the conversion by (python/python3):
```
python -m convertion
```
